{"data":[{"name":"99:1","price":"Ҳангоме ки замин бо шадидтарин таконҳояш ба ларза дарояд","arabic":"إِذَا زُلۡزِلَتِ ٱلۡأَرۡضُ زِلۡزَالَهَا","category":["99 (Az-Zalzalah)","Az-Zalzalah","Surah Az-Zalzalah"],"ayahNumber":6139,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"tg","meta":{"transliteration":"idhā zul'zilati al-arḍu zil'zālahā ","translations":["When","is shaken","the earth","(with) its earthquake","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["idhā","zul'zilati","al-arḍu","zil'zālahā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,690],[2,690,1730],[3,1730,2580],[4,2580,4295]]}},{"name":"99:2","price":"Ва замин борҳои сангинашро берун резад","arabic":"وَأَخۡرَجَتِ ٱلۡأَرۡضُ أَثۡقَالَهَا","category":["99 (Az-Zalzalah)","Az-Zalzalah","Surah Az-Zalzalah"],"ayahNumber":6140,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"tg","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-akhrajati al-arḍu athqālahā ","translations":["And brings forth","the earth","its burdens","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-akhrajati","al-arḍu","athqālahā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1380],[2,1380,2170],[3,2170,3865]]}},{"name":"99:3","price":"Ва инсон мегӯяд: «Он [замин]-ро чӣ шудааст?»","arabic":"وَقَالَ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ مَا لَهَا","category":["99 (Az-Zalzalah)","Az-Zalzalah","Surah Az-Zalzalah"],"ayahNumber":6141,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"tg","meta":{"transliteration":"waqāla al-insānu mā lahā ","translations":["And says","man","What","(is) with it","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["waqāla","al-insānu","mā","lahā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,930],[2,930,3310],[3,3310,3790],[4,3790,4495]]}},{"name":"99:4","price":"Дар он рӯз [замин] тамоми хабарҳояшро бозгӯ мекунад","arabic":"يَوۡمَئِذٖ تُحَدِّثُ أَخۡبَارَهَا","category":["99 (Az-Zalzalah)","Az-Zalzalah","Surah Az-Zalzalah"],"ayahNumber":6142,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"tg","meta":{"transliteration":"yawma-idhin tuḥaddithu akhbārahā ","translations":["That Day","it will report","its news","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["yawma-idhin","tuḥaddithu","akhbārahā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2180],[2,2180,3220],[3,3220,4875]]}},{"name":"99:5","price":"Зеро Парвардигорат ба ӯ [чунин] ваҳй [ва ҳукм] кардааст","arabic":"بِأَنَّ رَبَّكَ أَوۡحَىٰ لَهَا","category":["99 (Az-Zalzalah)","Az-Zalzalah","Surah Az-Zalzalah"],"ayahNumber":6143,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"tg","meta":{"transliteration":"bi-anna rabbaka awḥā lahā ","translations":["Because","your Lord","inspired","[to] it","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["bi-anna","rabbaka","awḥā","lahā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1750],[2,1750,2690],[3,2690,3560],[4,3560,4215]]}},{"name":"99:6","price":"Дар он рӯз мардум гурӯҳ-гурӯҳ бозмегарданд, то [натиҷаи] аъмолашон ба онон нишон дода шавад","arabic":"يَوۡمَئِذٖ يَصۡدُرُ ٱلنَّاسُ أَشۡتَاتٗا لِّيُرَوۡاْ أَعۡمَٰلَهُمۡ","category":["99 (Az-Zalzalah)","Az-Zalzalah","Surah Az-Zalzalah"],"ayahNumber":6144,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"tg","meta":{"transliteration":"yawma-idhin yaṣduru al-nāsu ashtātan liyuraw aʿmālahum ","translations":["That Day","will proceed","the mankind","(in) scattered groups","to be shown","their deeds","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["yawma-idhin","yaṣduru","al-nāsu","ashtātan","liyuraw","aʿmālahum",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2010],[2,2010,2830],[3,2830,4460],[4,4460,5540],[5,5540,6560],[6,6560,8515]]}},{"name":"99:7","price":"Пас, ҳар кас ба андозаи заррае кори нек анҷом дода бошад, [подоши] онро мебинад","arabic":"فَمَن يَعۡمَلۡ مِثۡقَالَ ذَرَّةٍ خَيۡرٗا يَرَهُۥ","category":["99 (Az-Zalzalah)","Az-Zalzalah","Surah Az-Zalzalah"],"ayahNumber":6145,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"tg","meta":{"transliteration":"faman yaʿmal mith'qāla dharratin khayran yarahu ","translations":["So whoever","does","(equal to the) weight","(of) an atom","good","will see it","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["faman","yaʿmal","mith'qāla","dharratin","khayran","yarahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,580],[2,580,2140],[3,2140,3250],[4,3250,4250],[5,4250,5050],[6,5050,7025]]}},{"name":"99:8","price":"Ва ҳар кас ба андозаи заррае кори бад карда бошад, [кайфари] онро мебинад","arabic":"وَم